data.title: Morocco’s Renault Records Historic Results in 2023
meta_keywords: Morocco automotive industry among leaders in the field

data.meta_description: Morocco’s Renault Group has announced, through its Director and Industrial Pole Coordinator Mohamed Bachiri, exceptional financial performance for the year 2023, exceeding all expectations and setting new records in several key areas.
